EU Sees 40 New Europe Nuclear Plants by 2030, Sueddeutsche Says

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-12-09T00:01:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-09/eu-sees-40-new-europe-nuclear-plants-by-2030-sueddeutsche-says.html
The European Union sees nuclear
energy as “an important factor” and forecasts that as many as
40 new plants will be built in  Europe  between now and 2030, even
as  Germany  has decided to exit nuclear power,  Sueddeutsche
Zeitung  reported, citing a draft document by EU Energy
Commissioner  Guenther Oettinger .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  